OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Courts are set to be given powers to   
OL,6, hand out tougher punishments for       
OL,7, serious animal cruelty crimes, under   
OL,8, proposed new sentencing guidelines.    
OL,10,FUpdated guidance in England and Wales  
OL,11,Fwill affect sentences for crimes like  
OL,12,Fcausing unnecessary suffering, tail    
OL,13,Fdocking and animal fighting.           
OL,15,FCruelty for money, as part of organised
OL,16,Fcrime or particularly "sadistic" cases,
OL,17,Fwill be considered the most serious.   
OL,19,FIt follows the maximum penalty being   
OL,20,Fraised in 2021 to five years in prison.
